<h2><em><strong>Do you enjoy playing football? Join Butler Women's Football Club! </strong></em></h2><h3>All abilities are welcome,&nbsp;whether you've never kicked a ball before or you consider yourself a pro, come join us!&nbsp;The only requirement is that you enjoy playing!</h3><h3>We play in the Women's Football Premiership and we're also in the Floodlit and Trophy knock-out competitions.</h3><h3>If you would like to know more, please contact the club president (a.r.poole@dur.ac.uk), or alternatively just come along to training! We train on a Wednesday afternoon on the field behind Milfield.</h3><p><em>Photo-&nbsp;Butler Women's Football Club 13/14</em></p><p>&nbsp;<img src="https://scontent-a-lhr.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/r90/10454330_10154236685015464_746865834169495826_n.jpg?oh=c290144ca0303fdd8b69b76785f635d8&amp;oe=546CEE8C" alt="" width="671" height="503" /></p>